  stimulus_text = 'The narrator is a young girl who has just moved to the city with her family. She finds the city to be a very different place than the countryside she is used to.  "The sights and sounds of the city were a cacophony of noise and light.  I was overwhelmed by the rush of people and the constant movement.  I missed the quiet of the country, where I could hear the birds singing in the trees and the wind rustling through the leaves."  What is the main idea of this passage?',
