  stimulus_text = 'The author is trying to convey the important message that every person has the ability to make a difference in the world, no matter how big or small. The author uses a simple metaphor to illustrate this idea, comparing the world to a river.  The author uses vivid imagery and figurative language to help readers connect with the message.  What is the most likely reason why the writer uses the river as a metaphor?',
